code: @Override protected PutRollupJobRequest doParseInstance(final XContentParser parser) throws IOException {     final String optionalId = randomBoolean() ? jobId : null.     return new PutRollupJobRequest(RollupJobConfig.fromXContent(parser, optionalId)). }
